</span> ("two plus two equals four")</dd>
<dd id="mwPw"><span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt297" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"1 + 2 = 3"}}' id="mwQA"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle 1+2=3}">
