  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/43f7e9a80913b9d5ec8d169140265d3e2fff5b4b" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.505ex; width:9.426ex; height:2.343ex;" alt="{\displaystyle 1+2=3}"/></span><span about="#mwt297">
</span> ("one plus two equals three")</dd>
<dd id="mwQQ"><span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt299" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"5 + 4 + 2 = 11"}}' id="mwQg"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle 5+4+2=11}">
